title: Michael Rizzo Chessman video on social justice issues in the USA
description:
Mr. Michael Rizzo Chessman, founder of several websites and related initiatives
such as a global ad campaign a decade ago on issues concerning improved cultural
access and ties along with better use of the English language as a standard
and universal Health care coverage for all decently spirited folks speaks
to some of the issues here in this 40 minute video from around 2005 - 2006

Thanks for downloading

Michael Rizzo Chessman
